{"tid":1632644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非] 整唔到百萬大遊行 點解唔整多次823級數既大型人鏈","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:47:11.000Z","uid":272866,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b16528db31815a226b97fc3c13335e3ae1d56008","tid":1632644,"uid":272866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:17:23.000Z","msg":"勇武繼續升級，但係和理非升級唔到，先會令到公眾既關注去左裝飾定裝修<br />\n<br />\n和理非最大既困難，在於重現唔到609 616 818呢個level既百萬和平遊行<br />\n<br />\n要國際去制裁港共黑警，就唔可以比外國覺得我地真係暴徒，要諗辦法增加和理非活動既矚目程度<br />\n<br />\n既然612 class既遊行整唔到，點解唔重現多次823級數既大型人鏈？<br />\n<br />\n搵下日頭整，823 20萬人都可以做到港島新界九龍，人多既話可以整雙人鏈，40萬人穿全香港<br />\n<br />\n易做，又可以吸引國際關注，避免媒體成日focus暴力<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師唔該集思廣益，諗多d有創意既抗爭方法"},{"pid":"1a3ddc52398c83dd5ffd6d11a5c7f2a74376c5fc","tid":1632644,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a488f446b921ba001dac8a3b740da444d6dad3","tid":1632644,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:19:29.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8e8c0985acc3dad0f92974dc17aac1d1230c06e","tid":1632644,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:20:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>是否由香港政府所策劃的恐怖襲擊 ?? <br />\n的士撞入示威人群謀殺示威民眾及激起對立</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632301\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632301</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1x3QsW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1x3QsW.jpg&h=e15c60f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"405e4b5806453aa2a2d6d69f2ac21943a4c1eb0c","tid":1632644,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:38.000Z","msg":"唔知點解次次討論整人鍊都推唔郁架.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8073f936bfb5cb39f35c2f7cab02cdc997ceb043","tid":1632644,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"或者我地可以唸下一齊排隊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分和勇，入左黎先，攞番國際輿論又唔駛不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632602-\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632602-</a> 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8bd6b4c180b4cfb2c574de74b21bdb692492b0e","tid":1632644,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4253cda1cd5974bf3ca6e0345e83290d70be2b","tid":1632644,"uid":40585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n因為交通問題 真係好難再做大遊行<br />\n人鏈大家落屋企樓下就做到<br />\n易做易散"}]}